title: Boys, girls STAC finals matchups set
text:
Boys, girls STAC finals matchups set 
By wbng sports October 17, 2015 Updated Oct 17, 2015 at 11:48 PM EDT 
(WBNG Binghamton) Ithaca scored two first half goals and tacked on four more in the second half to breeze past Oneonta, 6-0, and earn a spot in the STAC finals on Monday. Ithaca will play Vestal, which beat Johnson City, 1-0, in extra time. On the girls' side, Chenango Forks shut out Elmira, 3-0, to advance to play Vestal in the final.
